letters.love: I wish that you always stay close to me and keep making me feel lucky every day.;It is difficult to imagine my life without you because you are the one who rules it.;I promise to always be there for you, to keep you happy and smiling.;Thank you for choosing and loving me beyond conditions.;Whenever I am with you, every moment feels extra special.;I have found the love of my life and my best friend in you.I was so alone in this whole wide world, but I found a companion for life in you when you arrived.
